        </p>

        <p>
          Aside from bioinformatics, <strong>I love diving deep into machine learning</strong>, especially ML for science, NLP, and language models. Lately exploring <strong>knowledge graphs, distillation, and inference optimisation</strong>. I also love working with <strong>structural biology data</strong>, especially protein structures (perhaps thanks to my undergrad thesis).
        </p>

        <p>
          Away from the terminals, <strong>I love wet lab work</strong>, especially related to cell culture and molecular stuff. I have always found tactile work enjoyable. In my free time, I do photography, filmmaking, and writing.
        </p>

